    "This association persisted even after controlling for various comorbidities associated with ADRD (HR 0.79, 95% CI 0.58-1.07).",
    "However, it did not reach statistical significance at the conventional 0.05 level.",
    "The comorbidities include delirium, intellectual disability, aphasia, depression, anxiety, bipolar disorder, hypertension, hyperlipidemia, vitamin B12 deficiency, and cardiovascular disease (Fig. 5c).",
    "Additionally, among the 978 patients diagnosed with ADRD, 411 reported receiving Manual therapy techniques, while 1402 MCI patients without ADRD reported the same intervention.",
    "Fisher's exact test demonstrated a statistically significant difference in the utilization of Manual therapy techniques between the ADRD and non-ADRD groups (p < 0.001)."
